    public interface ConceptModelComponent
extends org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject
    A representation of the model object 'Concept Model Component'. Abstract base class for various concept model components.

    The following features are supported:

    • Uuid
    • Active
    • Effective Time
    • Author

    See Also:
    MrcmPackage.getConceptModelComponent()
